rows.label: qst001401_msg0001
rows.name:
Argh, why can't the Superbian
army be more speedy, mo?

rows.label: qst001401_msg0002
rows.name:
At this rate, my precious cargo
will spoil before I can get
it to the capital, mo...

rows.label: qst001401_msg0003
rows.name:
Ooh! A Driver who looks like they
have time on their hands, mo!

rows.label: qst001401_msg0004
rows.name:
Driver-san, please take
on a request, mo!

rows.label: qst001401_msg0005
rows.name:
The cargo that arrives here at Ananyam Harbor is
transported to the lower level of the capital, Alba
Margen, through the Cargo Transportation Zone up ahead, mo.

rows.label: qst001401_msg0006
rows.name:
But right now, the Cargo Transportation Zone
is overrun with Land Volffs and Noog Skeeters,
so we can't transport the cargo safely, mo.

rows.label: qst001401_msg0007
rows.name:
I asked the Superbian army to clear
them out, but it looks like it's
going to take a while, mo...

rows.label: qst001401_msg0008
rows.name:
So, I'd like to ask you,
who look very capable, mo.

rows.label: qst001401_msg0009
rows.name:
If you can do it speedily,
the reward will be generous,
mo! Will you do it, mo?

rows.label: qst001401_msg0010
rows.name:
Such a speedy decision
is wonderful, mo!

rows.label: qst001401_msg0011
rows.name:
Well then, I need you to defeat the
Land Volffs and Noog Skeeters in the
Cargo Transportation Zone, mo.
